des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “AIRIA” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “AIRIA” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “AIRIA” skill, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on air conditioner.
Alexa, turn off air purifier.
Alexa, set air conditioner to 20 degrees.
Alexa, set air purifier speed to low.
